page.title: 20MELBOURNE'S SUBSCRIBERS.
page.content: MELBOURNE JUNIOR SCHOOL WOULD LIKE TO THANK THE FOLLOWING MEMBERS OF STAFF AND CHILDREN WHO HELPED TO COMPILE THE ENTRIES IN THIS DOMESDAY PROJECT.MR. WOOLLEY,MRS.BENTLEY,MR.BULLAS,MR. SLATER,MRS.SHONE,MRS.JEFFREYS,MRS. LOMAS,MRS.UZZELL & MRS.HORSFALL.STUART WOODMAN,WILLIAM STANLEY,RUTH SLATER,HOWARD CHESHIRE,EDWARD PARKER, CHRIS CHMIEL,GARY JACKSON,PETER GEORGIOU,WAYNE HAWKSWORTH,MELANIE MOORE,RICHARD BENFIELD,JOANNE YOUNGER, SUSAN TALBOT,PAUL BAILEY,PAUL COOKE, CALVIN SMITH,MARC ESSEX,DANIEL MURFIN, KATHRYN WRIGHT,ZOE EATON,MARC SANDERS, AMANDA GIBBS,LAURA HAND,ELONOR TIVEY, ALLISON GRIFFITHS,ANGELA JOHNSON, CATHERINE BOSWORTH,ALL OF CLASS 2 AND THE WHOLE OF CLASS 6.YOUR EFFORTS HAVE MADE MY JOB OF COLLATING ALL THE MATERIAL THAT MUCH EASIER.MANY THANKS TO ALL OF YOU.MR.BELL.
